          <hi rend="grantha">s<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">va</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">sti</supplied> śrī</hi>
        </p>
        <p>
                    kō-v-irācak<choice>
            <sic>o</sic>
            <corr>ē</corr>
          </choice>cari-paruma<choice>
            <orig>k=ku</orig>
            <reg>rk=ku</reg>
          </choice> yāṇṭu pati<choice>
            <orig>n</orig>
            <reg>ṉ</reg>
          </choice><choice>
            <sic>a</sic>
            <corr>ai</corr>
          </choice>ñc-āvatu
                </p>
        <p>
                    Uṟattūr-<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>-kūṟṟat
                    <milestone break="no" n="b" unit="block"/>
                    <supplied reason="lost">tu</supplied>
                    <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/>
                </p>
        <p>
                    <lb n="2" style="text-align: left"/>
                    <milestone n="a" unit="block"/>
                    naṅkaiyār Aṉantam paḻiyili vaḻiyu
                </p>
      </div>
      <div type="apparatus">
        <listApp>
          <app loc="1">
            <lem>
              <hi rend="grantha">s<unclear reason="eccentric_ductus">va</unclear><supplied reason="omitted">sti</supplied></hi>
            </lem>
            <note>The letter <foreign>va</foreign> looks like <foreign>pa</foreign>.</note>
          </app>
          <app loc="1">
            <lem>-paruma<choice>
                <orig>k=ku</orig>
                <reg>rk=ku</reg>
              </choice></lem>
            <note>It seems that the engraver first wrote <foreign>kora</foreign> and, realising his mistake, transformed the <foreign>ra</foreign> into <foreign>ca</foreign>.</note>
          </app>
        </listApp>
      </div>
      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
        <p n="1">Fifteenth year of the king Rājakesarivarman.</p>
        <p n="1"><gap reason="lost"/> <supplied reason="lost">in the</supplied> Uṟattūrkkūṟṟam <gap reason="lost"/></p>
        <p n="2">Naṅkaiyār Aṉantam Paḻiyili <gap reason="ellipsis"/> <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>vaḻiyu</foreign>
          </supplied></p>
      </div>
      <div type="commentary">
        <p>The inscription stops short in line 2 after <foreign>vaḻiyu</foreign> and seems to have been left unfinished.</p>
        <p n="2">Naṅkaiyār Aṉantam Paḻiyili ("our unbounded and irreproachable lady"?) is possibly the donor.</p>
      </div>
